The blood-flowing conclusion! Chucky’s been on a murderous path of personal revenge… cutting a swath through everyone he’s got grudges against… now that he’s come up against someone that’s been preparing for him, will he leave this series alive?

description:
The Amazing Super Secret Origin Of The Explorers Of The Unknown!

Archie is reading a book called the Explorers of the Unknown, whose characters remind him of his friends in Riverdale. In the book, while working on a movie about his life, Red fights a giant robot that goes on a rampage. He is aided by 6 other experts in their fields, and they form The Explorers of the Unknown. Their first mission: stop Myron Pepperdinkle and his destructive robots.

Following Lono's ascension to warlord for the houses of the Trust, the last remaining Minutemen are activated as the players on both sides ready themselves for the endgame of their private war.

Introduction done by Darwyn Cooke.
name: Volume Ten

description: When a hero dies, Eddie Ellison's life is changed forever. And when he crosses paths with the super-teen media darlings, The HyperActives, that change isn't necessarily for the better. The Hypers only care about the spotlight, and they don't want to share it with a new member! It's non-stop action as the original Silverwing faces off against the bonecrushing brute force known as Bash! And The HyperActives are faced with their most lethal foes the Uberforce! The only problem is that they've been attacked in their own headquarters, and there isn't a TV camera in sight! Will they have time to call their press agent? Or with the deadly Dr. Uberkoff on their doorstep, is it already too late?! Stay tuned! Stay Hyper!

Eddie Ellison has inherited the powers of Silverwing and joined the teen super team the Hyperactives! Unfortunately it doesn't seem like the Hyperactives want a new member. So Eddie is left to face off against their archenemies, the Uberforce, on his own. Will the Hypers come to Eddie's rescue, or will they leave him out to dry?

It's convention season again! And for the Hyper-Actives, it means fierce rivalries, annoying fans and bad food! But it becomes an even bigger cluster-fest when the unstoppable Ultimato crashes the party. Can our team steal the spotlight and defeat this unbeatable foe before the other heroes at the con do? Will their new costumes stand up to rabid fan-scrutiny?

This is it! The fourth and final issue of the Hyper-Actives' first limited series comes to an implosive conclusion as the young team takes on their mentor, Alphaman! What set this off? Would Alphaman hit his own kids? Would the spoiled media darlings of the team have a chance against the Planet's Most Powerful Person? Will it be captured on film for all time? It's 32 pages of teeth corroding, blood-pumping, nuclear, brain damage! Stay tuned! Stay Hyper! Don't miss the controversial new series that set the internet message boards on fire!

name: The Dead Remember; Revenge of the Vengeful Avenger;

description:
Writer Ron Marz has revitalized Witchblade and is the architect behind the acclaimed First Born and Broken Trinity crossover events. Now, joined by artist Lee Moder (First Born: Aftermath, Painkiller Jane), Marz debuts DRAGON PRINCE, a four-part modern fantasy with equal doses of magic and martial arts mayhem.

Like a lot of teenagers, Aaron Chiang feels he’s never fit in, though he’s never known why. But all that changes when he learns the truth of his heritage: He is the Dragon Prince, last of his kind and heir to the bloodline of all dragons. Hunted to the brink of extinction by a secret society of wizards, dragonkind’s survival is now in Aaron’s hands.

Featuring spectacular covers by Jeff Johnson (Amazing Spider-Man), Stjepan Sejic (Witchblade) and David Finch (New Avengers)!

"CITY OF THE DEAD" Genevieve becomes more deeply entangled in the dangerous game she's playing with Julien and the Duke of Lorraine. Julien descends into the blackest depths of the catacombs beneath Paris for a horrific confrontation. And at last, the true identity of the Holy Grail is revealed.
name: City of the Dead

description: " Was Judas Iscariot really Christ's betrayer, or is the traditional version of his story somehow wrong? How does it tie into Julien's quest for the Holy Grail? Find out this issue, as Julien makes a startling discovery! Also, the Duke of Lorraine and King Louis engage in a political showdown that will decide the fate of France... and the world.
name: Most Beloved

description: "PATH TO EMPIRE" Julien's investigation into the mystery of the Grail leads him to a opulent party where he and the Duke of Lorraine finally meet. Romantic sparks begin to fly between Julien and Lorraine's daughter ? much to the annoyance of Genevieve, Julien's old flame! Meanwhile, the world slips further and further towards war...
name: Path to Empire

description: "VINE OF DAVID." At last Julien and Genevieve learn the family secret of the Duke of Lorraine. But they must pay a terrible price... The explosive conclusion of the third story arc of the critically acclaimed series.
name: Word of Life

description: Europe is at war. Julien and Genevieve must flee the Duke's country estate, but even if they make it out, can Julien trust Gen to stay by his side?
name: To Kiss and To Kill

description:
Featuring a complete look at the major Marvel events of the last five years, as narrated by Watcher, this is your chance to catch up on everything! Is it all connected? What’s next? These answers and more arrive in Marvel: Your Universe!

Plus, Marvel: Your Universe contains never-before-seen new handbook material!

And did we mention that this 32 page must-read comic is absolutely free? That’s right True Believers, Marvel: Your Universe is your guide to comics’ most popular universe and absolutely free!
